{"tid":1808470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post] 1月5號上水遊行!!!!!","createTime":"2020-01-02T11:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T14:32:58.000Z","uid":193713,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"07bfc1d8d5890284a3f6909e84f1b9c0ce078fae","tid":1808470,"uid":193713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KiR8RTR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKiR8RTR.jpg&h=15ec740c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/erap9Fx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ferap9Fx.jpg&h=8c66b79d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日期：5/1/2020<br />\n時間：1500<br />\n地點：上水一號花園(龍豐對面)<br />\n<br />\n我地一班北區居民睇到北區受到水賊蝗蟲長年滋擾，同埋根據以往經驗係農曆新年前兩三個星期前最嚴重，所以我地希望係上水搞番場和理非遊行，途經絕大部份水貨舖，令佢地關門大吉，蝗蟲水賊衝唔到刺走水貨，同埋引起大家對地區議題關注。<br />\n<br />\n跪求大家多多支持。驅逐蝗蟲保平安，趕走水賊賀新春！<br />\n<br />\n活動TG頻道：<a href=\"https://t.me/wedontlikegreygoodstrader\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwedontlikegreygoodstrader&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPi2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=2865af55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wedontlikegreygoodstrader</a><br />\n<br />\nSource:北區哨channel"},{"pid":"e005e32ae4b3052106f9f919e15c0b347aa12ae7","tid":1808470,"uid":193713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"我要見每個post都有人share<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb7c9e6c421882e9585852598f315a0e3de2a55","tid":1808470,"uid":106348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"aef18fdc77171a335be37c5733ee8feb140bb5a5","tid":1808470,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:34: